title: [PS3] 3D Ultra Mini Golf Adventures 2
description:
<a href="http://www.3dultraminigolf.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.3dultraminigolf.com/</a>

Putt your way through the highly anticipated sequel to one of the hottest minigolf games available for download, 3D Ultra MiniGolf Adventures 2! Swing through 50+ fun-filled courses loaded with challenging obstacles including moving platforms, surprise traps, or tricky jumps. Be the first to discover secret "hole-in-one" shots that seem virtually impossible! It's a race to the finish as you play through a myriad of competitions based in imaginative locations, from the ghostly Haunted Manor to a Manic Museum, or even a snow-filled Winter Wonderland! Step onto the green, and prove that your MiniGolf skills are up to par!
